name: Platter Castle
description: What started out as a sketch of a castle, became something way different when I decided to model the drawing in Cinema 4D.  I wanted to bring together a visual contrast of something thought of as old and combine it with a more modern and brightly colored world.  Made for my 2020 animation portfolio.(copyright)@davekiehl for personal use only. Find me on Instagram and Twitter @davekiehl
